    Class Description
    Client
    Client is used for connection to the server and starting the game After the game is started a Game board is instantiated
    GameBoard
    Game Board is created when a game is launched and data is passed from the server It creates Graphical User Interface and displays visual data for players
    GameSession
    Game session is created for each pair of clients connected.
    Server
    Server class is used by clients to connect to.
    Ship
    The ship class represents one ship in game
    Tile
    The tile class represents one tile on a game board Used mainly to determine which icon to display
